## 1. Solitaire Settings — The Foundation

![Princess Cut French Pavé Crown Ring — Blue Nile Studio 18K Yellow Gold](/images/princess-cut-french-pave-crown-ring-18k-yellow-gold.avif)

Solitaire settings show the princess diamond in its pure form — square geometry, four corners exposed, maximum light return without competing elements.

**Why solitaire is the default for princess cut:**
- All light enters and exits through the diamond face-up, no side stones compete
- The square shape reads clearly — especially important for princess which has a distinctive modern aesthetic
- V-prong placement on all four corners is easiest to verify and customize in solitaire settings
- Lower setting price leaves more budget for stone quality

