## 2. Pavé Settings — Band Diamonds Add Sparkle

![Princess Cut Engagement Ring Settings — Budget Guide Under $600](/images/princess-cut-engagement-ring-settings-budget-guide.avif)

Pavé settings line the band with small diamonds, adding sparkle context for the center stone. The center corners remain exposed — V-prong protection still required. Pavé adds 1/10 to 3/8 ct. tw. to total carat weight.

**[Petite Micropavé in 14k White Gold (1/10 ct. tw.) — $1,325](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-micropave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-10-ct-tw-item-195402?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
