## 5. Bezel Settings — Maximum Corner Protection

Bezel settings encircle the diamond in a metal rim. For princess cut, a four-sided bezel provides complete corner protection — eliminating the chipping risk entirely. Trade-off: the corners are not visible, which removes the sharp-edged aesthetic that makes princess distinctive.

**[Bezel Solitaire in 14K White Gold — $1,310](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-item-296642?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
Clean modern bezel in white gold. Full corner protection.

**[Bezel Solitaire in 14K Yellow Gold — $1,310](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-item-296643?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**

