**[Bezel Solitaire in Platinum — $1,550](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-296647?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
Platinum bezel — the most protective setting for active-lifestyle wearers.

**[Bezel Baguette Three-Stone in 14K White Gold (JA) — $2,720](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/bezel-straight-baguette-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-316318?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**
